  • Constructor Details

    • UpdateAfterDrawMessage

      public UpdateAfterDrawMessage(ClientCard drawnCard, ClientFace newTopDeck, ClientCard newFaceUpCard, String username, int boardPosition)
      Constructs an UpdateAfterDrawMessage with the drawnCard, newTopDeck, newFaceUpCard, username and boardPosition provided.
      Parameters:
      drawnCard - the drawn card.
      newTopDeck - the new card that replaces the previous card that was present in the deck.
      newFaceUpCard - the new face up card that replaces the previous one.
      username - the username of the player who performs the drawing.
      boardPosition - the position from which the card was selected, 4 for golden deck, 5 for resource deck and 0, 1, 2 or 3 for face up cards.
